OL,3,CIn Pictures: Stars grace the red
OL,4,Ccarpet at the 98th Academy Awards
OL,6,FFor Hollywood's biggest night,
OL,7,Fcelebrities pay as much attention to
OL,8,Ftheir red-carpet attire as their
OL,9,Fspeeches. It's a night to leave a mark
OL,10,Fnot just on Hollywood but on best-
OL,11,Fdressed lists and even make fashion
OL,12,Fhistory.
OL,14,FColour dominated the Oscars red carpet
OL,15,Fas stars from Renate Reinsve to Chase
OL,16,FInfiniti stunned in their custom gowns
OL,17,Fahead of the ceremony on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
